name: The Irony of Kindergarten Dreamscape
description: "When we were kids, Indonesian people are told to draw a landscape of a peaceful scenery, build our dreams. Along the way, we grew up knowing the truth of many local animals will extinct with the fast development of industry. And when we hit our adult years, we tend to care less about our childhood memories, changing dreams into having luxurious living room.". 2160x2160 px. Made in 2021 by Toxic Motel. To celebrate the 76 years of Indonesia's independence day. Cheerz!
